Executive Summary 5



Troubles that occurred: 

1) The JSON script was not properly at first due to "the length of the string exceeds the value set on the maxJsonLength property". Had to change the JSON length to the max to make my script work.
2) The original source had about 1.3 million records and JSON conversion sites are not able to convert large CSV files. I had to split my CSV file into smaller files to be able to convert them into JSON.
3) The time column lead to my package failing due to the time column having several inaccurate data. Many of the data consisted of 2 digits numerical value instead of 4 digits numerical value. I changed the data type to varchar from time.
